task.description:
Single parametrized test replacing 3 separate tests (DevOps suggestion #3). Tests the flow_observability_context → events.jsonl chain end-to-end.
@pytest.fixture produces a tmp events dir. @pytest.mark.parametrize over: - flow_observability_context (CPU) → verify flow_start + flow_end in events.jsonl - gpu_flow_observability_context (mocked GPU) → verify heartbeat.json created - healthcheck_cpu.py → verify exit 0 with fresh events.jsonl, exit 1 without
One test function, 3 parametrized cases, catches all Layer 4+5 failures.
